  "body": "#### System information\r\n\r\nGeth version: `1.8.0-stable`\r\nOS & Version: all\r\n\r\n#### Expected behaviour\r\nIf a chain is synced in archive mode, i.e. `--gcmode archive`, once, this setting should be kept across client restarts, unless explicitly disabled.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behaviour\r\nThe default value, `--gcmode full` takes precedence over the previous setting unless `--gcmode archive` is explicitly set on each consecutive restart.",
